# Pocket Claude - Environment Configuration
#
# Authentication is handled automatically! Just run /login on first use.
# Credentials are saved to USB and work across all platforms.
#
# Only use this file if you need manual API key configuration.

# ============================================================
# RECOMMENDED: Automatic OAuth (Claude Pro/Max subscription)
# ============================================================
# No configuration needed! On first launch:
#   1. Run /login when prompted
#   2. Authenticate in browser
#   3. Credentials auto-saved to USB
#
# Works across Windows, macOS, and Linux - login once, use anywhere.
# Credentials stored in: config/.credentials.json

# ============================================================
# ALTERNATIVE: Manual API Key (pay-per-use billing)
# ============================================================
# Use this if you prefer API billing instead of subscription.
# Get your key at https://console.anthropic.com/
# Billed per token to your Anthropic Console account.
#
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-xxxxx

# ============================================================
# ALTERNATIVE: Manual OAuth Token (subscription, no auto-refresh)
# ============================================================
# Use this if automatic login doesn't work on your system.
# To get your token:
#   1. Run: claude setup-token
#   2. Follow the prompts to authenticate
#   3. Copy the token (starts with sk-ant-oat01-)
#
# Note: This token may expire and won't auto-refresh.
#
# CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=sk-ant-oat01-xxxxx

# ============================================================
# Optional Settings
# ============================================================
# Set a custom model (defaults to claude-sonnet-4-20250514)
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
